{"word":"ἑρμηνεύω","slug":"ἑρμηνεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑρμηνεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἑρμηνεύς'><el>ἑρμηνεύς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to interpret</i> foreign tongues, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to interpret, put into words, give utterance to</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to explain</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}